      p
        | The active state should be removed once the user moves their pointer a significant distance from the button. This cancels the
        code "iostap"
        | event. Bringing the finger back to the button will re-instate the active class.
      p
        pre.
          .button {...}

          // Active styles
          .button.__active {...}
